intro_content: |
  <p>The Department for Levelling Up, Housing and Communities (DLUHC) is funding 
    English councils to collaboratively develop digital planning services as 
    part of the commitment to improve the planning system outlined in the 
    <a href="https://bills.parliament.uk/bills/3155">Levelling Up and Regeneration Bill</a>, 
    and aspirations for the future of local government services expressed in the 
   <a href="https://www.localdigital.gov.uk/what-is-the-declaration/">Local Digital Declaration</a>.</p>
content:
